alignment top_left
background yes
border_width 1
cpu_avg_samples 2
default_color black
default_outline_color black
default_shade_color black
draw_borders no
draw_graph_borders yes
draw_outline no
draw_shades no
use_xft yes
xftfont UbuntuMono:size=15
gap_x 25
gap_y 10
minimum_size 5 5
#maximum_width 1500
net_avg_samples 2
no_buffers yes
out_to_console no
out_to_stderr no
extra_newline no
own_window yes
own_window_class Conky
own_window_type override
own_window_transparent yes
stippled_borders 0
update_interval 1.0
uppercase no
use_spacer none
show_graph_scale no
show_graph_range no

TEXT
${color darkgrey}$hr$color
Uptime: $uptime
Temperature (in C): ${acpitemp}
CPU Usage: $cpu% ${cpubar 4}
Frequencies (GHz): ${freq_g 1} / ${freq_g 2} / ${freq_g 3} / ${freq_g 4}
RAM Usage: $mem of $memmax ($memperc%) ${membar 4}
Disk IO: read:$diskio_read / write:$diskio_write
Processes: $processes / Running: $running_processes
${color darkgrey}$hr$color
Power:
* adapter: $acpiacadapter
* battery: $battery_percent% ($battery_time) ${battery_bar 4}
${color darkgrey}$hr$color
Filesystems:
* sda: ${fs_used /} of ${fs_size /} - ${fs_used_perc /}% ${fs_bar 6 /}
${color darkgrey}$hr$color
Networking:
* wlp3s0 (${addr wlp3s0}): up:${upspeed wlp3s0} / down:${downspeed wlp3s0}
* enp0s25 (${addr enp0s25}): up:${upspeed enp0s25} / down:${downspeed enp0s25}
${color darkgrey}$hr$color
Top Processes      PID     CPU%   MEM%   IO%    TIME
* ${top name 1} ${top pid 1} ${top cpu 1} ${top mem 1} ${top io_perc 1} ${top time 1}
* ${top name 2} ${top pid 2} ${top cpu 2} ${top mem 2} ${top io_perc 2} ${top time 2}
* ${top name 3} ${top pid 3} ${top cpu 3} ${top mem 3} ${top io_perc 3} ${top time 3}
* ${top name 4} ${top pid 4} ${top cpu 4} ${top mem 4} ${top io_perc 4} ${top time 4}
* ${top name 5} ${top pid 5} ${top cpu 5} ${top mem 5} ${top io_perc 5} ${top time 5}
* ...
${color darkgrey}$hr$color

